Subject: drm/amdgpu: allow direct submission of PDE updates v2
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 807e2994092c0bd863c0141c99f5e3f807d4c7f8
